Package: rdocodeR
Title: RDoC Decoding and Circular Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alessio", "User", , "alessio@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for Research Domain Criteria (RDoC) analysis,
    including a ggplot2-based circular correlation plot, palette helpers,
    legend plotting utilities, and an optional decoding pipeline for
    FreeSurfer overlays.
